# equal

**Instance Property**

The callback used to compare values in the dictionary for equality. If `NULL`, the collection will use pointer equality to compare values in the collection. See [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CFDictionaryEqualCallBack] for a description of this callback.

## Declaration

```swift
var equal: CFDictionaryEqualCallBack!
```
